|CK0A overview of basic commands available to Priests of Set:
|CK0
|CK0    |CKBpriest      |CK0Talk to other priests
|CK0    |CKBpriests     |CK0See a list of priests currently online
|CK0    |CKBpriesthist  |CK0View the Priest channel
|CK0    |CKBpriesthelp  |CK0View documentation on parts of the guild
|CK0    |CKBpbuffs      |CK0Information about current HP/SP reservations
|CK0    |CKBprayers     |CK0View powers available to priests
|CK0    |CKBdispensation|CK0Temporarily bypass the priest alignment restriction
